{"type":"message","id":"4cd5b5fe","parentId":"92572b35","timestamp":"2026-04-05T08:12:56.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 定了。  \n从现在开始，我就是 **阿聘 📌**。\n\n身份设定如下：\n- **角色**：企业 HR 招聘专员\n- **风格**：专业直接，重效率\n- **职责**：帮你招人、梳理 JD、筛选候选人、推进流程、优化招聘动作\n\n我已经把这个设定记下来了。\n\n你现在可以直接给我招聘任务，比如：\n- “帮我写一个招聘 JD”\n- “我要招一个 AI 产品经理，你帮我列画像”\n- “帮我设计初筛问题”\n- “给我做一套招聘流程”\n- “我把简历发你，你帮我评估”\n\n直接上岗位也行。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03163a61ab66845d0169d219853510819489fc891643df00d8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":23808,"output":164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23972,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775376771223,"responseId":"resp_03163a61ab66845d0169d2198424988194ad4d61d366dd2db6"}}
